```plantuml
@startuml hyeonsangjeon_youtube-dl-nas
skinparam backgroundColor #ffffff
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #f3f3f3
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam lifelineBackgroundColor #f3f3f3
skinparam lifelineBorderColor #000000

actor User
participant "Web Interface\n(Bottle)" as WebInterface
participant "REST API\n(Bottle)" as RestAPI
participant "Queue Manager" as QueueManager
participant "Download Worker\n(yt-dlp/youtube-dl)" as DownloadWorker
participant "WebSocket" as WebSocket
database "Auth.json" as Auth

User -> WebInterface: Access Login Page
WebInterface -> Auth: Validate Credentials
Auth --> WebInterface: Authentication Success/Failure
WebInterface -> User: Login Success/Failure

User -> WebInterface: Submit Download Request
WebInterface -> QueueManager: Add Request to Queue

WebInterface -> WebSocket: Open Connection
WebSocket -> User: Real-time Updates

User -> RestAPI: Submit Download Request (ID/Password)
RestAPI -> Auth: Validate Credentials
Auth --> RestAPI: Authentication Success/Failure
RestAPI -> QueueManager: Add Request to Queue (if authenticated)

loop Process Queue
    QueueManager -> DownloadWorker: Fetch Request
    DownloadWorker -> QueueManager: Download Status
    QueueManager -> WebSocket: Notify Status/Progress
end

WebSocket -> User: Notify Completion

@enduml
```